<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Songsan's Photo Diary</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm mb-4">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/">📸 Photo Diary</a>
        <div class="d-flex">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2" onclick="location.href='/mypage'">마이페이지</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#orderModal">게시글 인쇄 요청</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2" onclick="location.href='/order'">인쇄 주문 목록</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary fw-bold" onclick="location.href='/post/new'">
                <i class="bi bi-plus-lg"></i> 새 일기 쓰기
            </button>

        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row pt-3 align-items-end mb-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-start">
            <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">Image Logs</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">송산님의 소중한 순간들을 기록합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-md-end gap-2">
                <a href="/" class="badge rounded-pill {{^selectedTag}}bg-primary{{/selectedTag}}{{#selectedTag}}bg-white text-dark border{{/selectedTag}} text-decoration-none px-3"># 전체</a>

                <a href="/?tag=여행" class="badge rounded-pill bg-white text-dark border text-decoration-none px-3"># 여행</a>
                <a href="/?tag=일상" class="badge rounded-pill bg-white text-dark border text-decoration-none px-3"># 일상</a>
                <a href="/?tag=맛집" class="badge rounded-pill bg-white text-dark border text-decoration-none px-3"># 맛집</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        {{#posts}}
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card diary-card shadow-sm border-0 h-100" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="location.href='/post/detail/{{id}}'">

                    <div class="position-relative">
                        {{#firstImageUrl}}
                            <img src="{{firstImageUrl}}" class="card-img-top diary-card-img" alt="Diary Image">
                        {{/firstImageUrl}}
                        {{^firstImageUrl}}
                            <div class="bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center diary-card-img">
                                <i class="bi bi-image text-muted" style="font-size: 3rem;"></i>
                            </div>
                        {{/firstImageUrl}}

                        {{#mood}}<span class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-2 badge rounded-pill bg-white shadow-sm text-dark" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">{{.}}</span>{{/mood}}
                    </div>

                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-dark text-truncate">{{title}}</h5>

                        <p class="card-text text-secondary mb-2" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">
                            <i class="bi bi-person"></i> {{author}} <span class="mx-1">|</span> <i class="bi bi-calendar3"></i> {{getFormattedDate}}
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-2">
                            {{#tag}} <span class="badge bg-light text-primary border">#{{tag}}</span>
                            {{/tag}}
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted text-truncate-3 small">
                            {{content}}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/posts}}

        {{^posts}}
            <div class="col-12 text-center py-5">
                <i class="bi bi-journal-x display-1 text-muted"></i>
                <h4 class="mt-4 text-muted">아직 작성된 다이어리가 없어요.</h4>
                <p class="text-secondary">첫 번째 일기를 작성하고 추억을 기록해 보세요!</p>
            </div>
        {{/posts}}
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="orderModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="orderModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content shadow">
            <div class="modal-header border-0">
                <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="orderModalLabel">📦 인쇄 및 배송 요청</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>

            <form action="/order/request" method="post" id="orderForm">
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="px-2 mb-3">
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="receiverName" class="form-label fw-bold">수령인 성함</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="receiverName" name="receiverName"
                                       placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="phoneNumber" class="form-label fw-bold">연락처</label>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phoneNumber" name="phoneNumber"
                                       placeholder="010-0000-0000" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="px-2 mb-4">
                        <label for="shippingAddress" class="form-label fw-bold">배송지 주소</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="shippingAddress" name="shippingAddress"
                               placeholder="예: 서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 123" required>
                        <p class="text-muted small mt-2">포토북을 배송받으실 정확한 주소를 입력해주세요.</p>
                    </div>

                    <hr class="my-4">

                    <div class="px-2">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">인쇄할 다이어리 선택</h6>
                            <div class="form-check">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="selectAll">
                                <label class="form-check-label small fw-bold" for="selectAll">전체 선택</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row g-2" id="printList" style="max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto;">
                            {{#posts}}
                                <div class="col-12">
                                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm print-item-card mb-2" style="cursor: pointer; background-color: #f8f9fa;" onclick="toggleCheck('{{id}}')">
                                        <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center py-2">
                                            <div class="form-check me-3">
                                                <input class="form-check-input print-checkbox" type="checkbox"
                                                       name="selectedPostIds" value="{{id}}" id="check-{{id}}"
                                                       onclick="event.stopPropagation(); updateCount();">
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="flex-grow-1 overflow-hidden">
                                                <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold text-truncate" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">{{title}}</h6>
                                                <small class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">{{formattedDate}}</small>
                                            </div>
                                            {{#tag}}
                                                <span class="badge bg-white text-primary border small ms-2">#{{.}}</span>
                                            {{/tag}}
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            {{/posts}}
                            {{^posts}}
                                <div class="text-center py-4 text-muted">선택 가능한 다이어리가 없습니다.</div>
                            {{/posts}}
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-end mt-2">
                            <small class="text-primary fw-bold" id="selectedCount">0개 선택됨</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="modal-footer border-0">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-light" data-bs-dismiss="modal">취소</button>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-4 fw-bold">주문 확정</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/index_request_print.js"></script>
</body>
</html>